# 15. AI System Architecture

## Vision

The AI subsystem is designed as a collection of specialized agents coordinated by a central AI Orchestrator.

Rather than sending all GitHub data to one prompt, each agent focuses on a specific task and produces structured outputs that are combined into a final Developer Intelligence Report.

This approach improves:

- Explainability
- Accuracy
- Maintainability
- Scalability
- Cost optimization

