# 28. Design Principles

Every AI output must:

- Be evidence-backed
- Include confidence scores
- Avoid unsupported claims
- Explain reasoning
- Be reproducible

No agent should make assumptions without repository evidence.

---

# 29. Future AI Evolution

Future versions may include:

- Code Quality Agent
- System Design Agent
- Open Source Contribution Agent
- AI Interview Agent
- Team Compatibility Agent
- Engineering Benchmark Agent
- Developer Personality Insights (based only on observable collaboration patterns, with clear limitations)
- Enterprise Hiring Agent

The architecture is intentionally modular so new agents can be added without affecting existing components.